reviewText: This video is homemade.  Absolutely no information is given.  It doesn't tell you what state it is filmed in!  Bought it for my hubby for Christmas and he asked if I could return it!!!  This video is worthless and a rip off.

Wonderful movie! It is like you are right there with them. Whether you

Non stop - No interruptions - and super footage of "book class bucks"!!
One of the best mule deer videos I have seen in years!
